      "endLine": 330,
      "endCol": 55
    },
    {
      "text": "/** Get the current native message index. Use this to capture a position\n   * that can later be passed to truncateMessages.\n   */\n  getNativeMessageIdx(): NativeMessageIdx",
      "contextualizedText": "// node/core/src/providers/provider-types.ts \u003e interface Agent \u003e method getNativeMessageIdx\n\n/** Get the current native message index. Use this to capture a position\n   * that can later be passed to truncateMessages.\n   */\n  getNativeMessageIdx(): NativeMessageIdx",
      "headingContext": "node/core/src/providers/provider-types.ts \u003e interface Agent \u003e method getNativeMessageIdx",
      "startLine": 332,
      "startCol": 3,
      "endLine": 335,
      "endCol": 42
    },
    {
