      "text": "/** Abort the current operation.\n   * Returns a promise that resolves when the abort is complete.\n   * - If streaming: resolves when the stream is terminated\n   * - If not streaming: resolves immediately\n   */\n  abort(): Promise\u003cvoid\u003e",
      "contextualizedText": "// node/core/src/providers/provider-types.ts \u003e interface Agent \u003e method abort\n\n/** Abort the current operation.\n   * Returns a promise that resolves when the abort is complete.\n   * - If streaming: resolves when the stream is terminated\n   * - If not streaming: resolves immediately\n   */\n  abort(): Promise\u003cvoid\u003e",
      "headingContext": "node/core/src/providers/provider-types.ts \u003e interface Agent \u003e method abort",
      "startLine": 346,
      "startCol": 3,
