      "endCol": 25
    },
    {
      "text": "/** Transition from stopped/tool_use to stopped/aborted.\n   * Call this after providing all tool results during an abort.\n   * @throws Error if not in stopped/tool_use state\n   */\n  abortToolUse(): void",
      "contextualizedText": "// node/core/src/providers/provider-types.ts \u003e interface Agent \u003e method abortToolUse\n\n/** Transition from stopped/tool_use to stopped/aborted.\n   * Call this after providing all tool results during an abort.\n   * @throws Error if not in stopped/tool_use state\n   */\n  abortToolUse(): void",
